  "title": "Installation Technician",
  "description": "<p>As our business expands, we’re seeking a skilled installation technician to join us. The ideal candidate will bring hands-on technical expertise. Responsibilities include system setup, troubleshooting primarily involving precision laser technologies. Strong communication and problem-solving skills are essential, along with the flexibility to adapt in fast-paced environments. </p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Key skills</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Technical Expertise:</strong> Proficient in reading and interpreting technical drawings, blueprints, and manuals.</li>\n  <li><strong>Installation:</strong> Skilled in assembling and installing industrial machinery and equipment according to specifications.</li>\n  <li><strong>Troubleshooting:</strong> Strong problem-solving skills to diagnose and fix issues efficiently.</li>\n  <li><strong>Basic Electrical Knowledge</strong>: Understanding wiring, voltage, and safety protocols</li>\n  <li><strong>Tool Proficiency</strong>: Comfortable using hand tools, drills, multimeters, and cable testers</li>\n  <li><strong>System Setup</strong>: Ability to follow schematics and install devices like sensors, panels, or laser heads</li>\n  <li><strong>Mechanical Aptitude</strong>: Assembling mounts, brackets, and enclosures with precision</li>\n  <li><strong>Computer Literacy</strong>: Navigating installation software, firmware updates, and basic configuration<br>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Engineering related field of study.</li>\n  <li>Singaporean/Permanent resident</li>\n</ul>",
